OL,3,CStudent kills 9 in second Turkish
OL,4,Cschool shooting in two days
OL,6,FA student opened fire at a secondary
OL,7,Fschool in southeast Turkey on
OL,8,FWednesday, killing nine people and
OL,9,Fwounding 13 others, in the second such
OL,10,Fshooting in the country in two days.
OL,12,FThe 14-year-old gunman, who was also
OL,13,Fkilled, arrived at the school armed
OL,14,Fwith guns believed to belong to his
OL,15,Ffather, a retired police officer,
OL,16,FKahramanmaras provincial Governor
OL,17,FMukerrem Unluer said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
