CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776323120
OL,3,CStudent kills 9 in second Turkish
OL,4,Cschool shooting in two days
OL,6,FHe was carrying five firearms and
OL,7,Fseven magazines when he entered the
OL,8,Fschool and opened fire in two
OL,9,Fclassrooms.
OL,11,FThe victims included a teacher and
OL,12,Fthree students from the Ayser Calik
OL,13,FSecondary School, Unluer said.
OL,15,FAt least six of the wounded were in
OL,16,Fserious condition. Authorities have
OL,17,Fnot yet stated a motive for the attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
