PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776323120
OL,3,CStudent kills 9 in second Turkish
OL,4,Cschool shooting in two days
OL,6,FThe attack came just a day after 16
OL,7,Fpeople, mostly students, were wounded
OL,8,Fwhen a former student opened fire at a
OL,9,Fhigh school in nearby Sanliurfa
OL,10,Fprovince. The assailant later killed
OL,11,Fhimself.
OL,13,FUntil this week, such school shootings
OL,14,Fwere rare in Turkey.
OL,16,FState-run broadcaster TRT identified
OL,17,FWednesday's shooter as Isa Aras
OL,18,FMersinli and said his father was
OL,19,Fdetained for questioning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
