OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776323120
OL,3,CStudent kills 9 in second Turkish
OL,4,Cschool shooting in two days
OL,6,FTurkish authorities imposed a ban on
OL,7,Fthe broadcast of "traumatic" images
OL,8,Ffrom the shooting, warning media
OL,9,Forganisations to limit coverage to
OL,10,Fstatements from officials.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FEarlier, media reports said that
OL,18,Fauthorities sent police and ambulances
OL,19,Fto the school in Kahramanmaras'
OL,20,FOnikisubat district, after gunfire was
OL,21,Fheard there.
