OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776323120
OL,3,CStudent kills 9 in second Turkish
OL,4,Cschool shooting in two days
OL,6,FImages from the scene showed at least
OL,7,Ftwo people being put into ambulances.
OL,9,FParents rushed to the school after
OL,10,Fhearing reports of an armed attack,
OL,11,FNTV television reported, adding that
OL,12,Fpolice took security measures around
OL,13,Fthe school.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
